{"tid":1475490,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[旗海戰略]係時候出埋歐盟旗","createTime":"2019-08-15T13:28:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T04:25:10.000Z","uid":215715,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"314709650f51ad37baaced79e75590f9b61aa71e","tid":1475490,"uid":215715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:28:27.000Z","msg":"有香港旗 有英國旗 有美國旗 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點解冇歐盟旗?</span><br />\n歐盟係第一個對林奠發出最高級別外交照會<br />\n第一個國家收政庇 收黃台仰幫義士著草提供案例<br />\n第一個對香港發出旅遊警示(愛爾蘭)<br />\n出正式聲明仲快過英國 硬過美國 <br />\n係時候多謝歐盟<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">烏克蘭當年廣場革命都係因為歐盟旗<br />\n先令示威者得到大量歐盟國家非戰略物資援助</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.euractiv.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2015/02/hungarians_protest_against_orban.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.euractiv.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2015%2F02%2Fhungarians_protest_against_orban.jpeg&h=023f8175&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.europeaninterest.eu/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Euromaidan.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.europeaninterest.eu%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2FEuromaidan.jpg&h=5517cfea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.vocaleurope.eu/wp-content/uploads/20140203PHT34627_original.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vocaleurope.eu%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F20140203PHT34627_original.jpg&h=f0e81fbb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.chathamhouse.org/sites/default/files/styles/teaser_800x480/public/images/2017-04-12-Maidan.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chathamhouse.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fteaser_800x480%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2017-04-12-Maidan.jpg&h=9b3f67e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/e315r3TiOL51LRSuKs0..g--~B/aD0yMjQxO3c9NDI5NjtzbT0xO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/ap_webfeeds/51a2daf47255ae28440f6a706700e989.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fe315r3TiOL51LRSuKs0..g--~B%2FaD0yMjQxO3c9NDI5NjtzbT0xO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fap_webfeeds%2F51a2daf47255ae28440f6a706700e989.jpg&h=1d9b4e09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n香港旗英國旗美國旗冇貨?<br />\n歐盟旗啦屌你</span></span>"},{"pid":"e5a3f1965fe79b5e6d21a248d4902476859c82b3","tid":1475490,"uid":76922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GkK6vjT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGkK6vjT.jpg&h=faa81d6c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EAOOJET.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEAOOJET.jpg&h=3b098cdf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R1rsZde.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR1rsZde.png&h=acaac433&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z3Pm3EU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ3Pm3EU.jpg&h=b70d27dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d03f802bc0e3d0b70256813ca53f81c58aefcc5","tid":1475490,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:32:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22917ecd2e21d29801b62e120b65ade577b5321b","tid":1475490,"uid":78971,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:32:33.000Z","msg":"要表示全世界文明國家都企喺我哋呢邊<br />\n818 遊行完，中共仲係強硬回應嘅<br />\n立即全面升級"},{"pid":"72331676a0635055d3cb844aea2c80a613c19af8","tid":1475490,"uid":66514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:36:55.000Z","msg":"拎埋北約旗啦，北約出手打殘北京"},{"pid":"4f628bbb0f3ced0f09fd5678304e650035098b46","tid":1475490,"uid":215715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:37:05.000